summary:
Oceanographer specialized in marine geology, whose works have contributed to mapping unexplored oceanic regions in Brazil, Wales and Iceland. 

Currently works at Deep BV, in Amsterdam, as data processing team leader.
Duties include data analysis, interpretation and reporting, project preparation, deliverables QC, client liaising, project personnel management and other processing related project management activities.
